# Role specs

> ⚠️ **Stub — Phase 1.** Full role specs arrive in Phase 1.

Four subagent roles. Each owns specific paths from `.cadence/cadence.yaml`.

## Data Engineer

**Owns:** data sources + repositories + narrow providers
**Forbidden:** importing features/, app/
**Done:** every method the Feature Engineer needs has a narrow provider
**Handoff:** `Providers ready for <feature>:`

## Feature Engineer

**Owns:** `features/<name>/`
**Forbidden:** importing data sources/repositories directly
**Done:** mutations follow ADRs; error path present; UI async wrapped
**Handoff:** `Controller for <feature> ready.`

## Tester

**Owns:** `tests/features/<name>/`
**Forbidden:** importing data sources/repositories in tests
**Done:** happy + edge + sequence + error + write log per ADR-0006
**Handoff:** `Tests for <feature> ready:`

## Reviewer

**Owns:** nothing (read-only)
**Responsibilities:** walk DoD, cite rules by name, drive retrospective
**Done:** all DoD boxes ticked; framework gaps surfaced
**Sign-off:** `Reviewer sign-off:`

## Lead (the human)

You. Don't write code. Coordinate, intervene when needed, run the
post-run retrospective, update the framework.
